title: Oct. 24: SUNY Orange roundup
text: Posted Oct. 25, 2015 at 2:00 AM Posted Oct. 25, 2015 at 2:00 AM » Social News Women’s volleyball Orange 3, Bronx 0 SUNY Orange: Colts prevailed 25-10, 25-14, 25-18; Sierra Hernandez 2 aces, 4 kills, 4 digs, 17 assists; Kayla Holterman 10 kills, 11 digs; Kayla VanPelt 11 kills, 4 digs, 2 blocks. Orange 3, Hostos 0 SUNY Orange: Colts (12-12, 12-6 Region XV) prevailed 25-18, 25-10, 25-18; Sierra Hernandez 4 kills, 4 digs, 12 assists; Kayla Holterman 4 aces, 13 kills, 4 digs, 1 block; Kayla VanPelt 1 ace, 11 kills, 4 digs, 3 blocks; Orange clinched Mid-Hudson Conference title by virtue of third tie-breaker (winning percentage of games) with SUNY Ulster. recordonline.com
